<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 06:22:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尼泊尔总理以印度为中心访华寻求投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pivot-india-nepal-pm-visits-china-seek-investment-2024-12-03/</link><description>尼泊尔资深共产主义政治家KP Sharma Oli今年第四次出任总理，他的目标是在对中国进行为期几天的访问期间说服北京为计划中的基础设施项目提供新动力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 06:10:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pivot-india-nepal-pm-visits-china-seek-investment-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>核协议失败30年后乌克兰敦促北约邀请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-pushes-nato-invite-30-years-after-failed-nuclear-deal-2024-12-03/</link><description>乌克兰周二猛烈抨击了30年前达成的一项协议，根据该协议，乌克兰放弃核武器以换取从未兑现的安全保证，同时乌克兰也在齐心推动加入北约联盟的邀请。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 06:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-pushes-nato-invite-30-years-after-failed-nuclear-deal-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国取消对澳大利亚肉类加工商的最终贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-final-trade-restrictions-australian-meat-processors-2024-12-03/</link><description>澳大利亚政府周二表示，中国取消了对澳大利亚两家肉类加工厂的贸易限制，允许全面恢复向该国出口红肉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 05:56:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-final-trade-restrictions-australian-meat-processors-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>香港特首表示高尔夫球场裁决不会影响公共住房计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-says-golf-course-ruling-will-not-hit-plans-public-housing-2024-12-03/</link><description>香港法院领导人李约翰 (John Lee) 周二表示，香港一家法院呼吁就在著名高尔夫球场部分地区建造 12,000 套公共住宅的计划重新进行公众咨询，这不会对该市的 10 年供应目标产生重大影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 05:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-says-golf-course-ruling-will-not-hit-plans-public-housing-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，台湾可能会在本周末开始军事演习，台湾正在密切关注中国航母的动向</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-watching-chinese-carrier-movements-sources-say-war-games-may-start-this-2024-12-03/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，正在监视中国航母的动向，并评估中国的军事活动，因为安全消息人士称，北京可能最早在本周末发起新的军事演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 04:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-watching-chinese-carrier-movements-sources-say-war-games-may-start-this-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>游说团体称，尽管有刺激措施，英国公司仍对中国业务持悲观态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/british-firms-downbeat-about-china-business-despite-stimulus-lobby-group-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>一项调查发现，在华经营的英国公司认为，由于经济形势低迷，过去一年在世界第二大经济体做生意变得更加困难，他们预计这种情况将持续到2025年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 02:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/british-firms-downbeat-about-china-business-despite-stimulus-lobby-group-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市在华尔街的带动下攀升；人民币、欧元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-03/</link><description>隔夜华尔街股市创下历史新高后，亚洲股市周二在表现优异的科技股领涨下上涨，而美元兑日元则徘徊在六周低点附近，交易员权衡美国和日本的利率前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 02:46:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>大宗商品贸易巨头嘉吉计划裁员约 8,000 人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cargill-plans-cut-around-5-global-employees-internal-memo-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>全球贸易公司嘉吉公司周二表示，由于农作物价格触及多年低点，其最近一个财年的收入大幅下滑，该公司计划裁员约 5%，即约 8,000 个工作岗位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 01:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cargill-plans-cut-around-5-global-employees-internal-memo-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>公司表示，埃克森美孚在圭亚那拍卖中继续就浅水区块进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-talks-continue-shallow-water-block-guyana-auction-company-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>埃克森美孚发言人周一表示，美国石油巨头埃克森美孚及其合作伙伴正在继续与圭亚那政府就开发浅水石油区块的条款进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:48:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-talks-continue-shallow-water-block-guyana-auction-company-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾抱怨后加拿大称太平洋贸易协定向新成员开放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-says-pacific-trade-pact-open-new-members-after-taiwan-complains-2024-12-03/</link><description>加拿大政府表示，一项主要的跨太平洋贸易协定仍然向包括台湾在内的其他有抱负的成员开放，此前台湾抱怨尚未成立一个工作组来考虑其加入。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-says-pacific-trade-pact-open-new-members-after-taiwan-complains-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>SEC 与 ICBC 部门就勒索软件攻击达成和解，但未处以罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/sec-settles-with-icbc-unit-over-ransomware-attack-imposes-no-fine-2024-12-02/</link><description>美国证券交易委员会已就 2023 年 11 月勒索软件攻击对中国工商银行一家子公司的记录保存指控达成和解，但决定不处以民事罚款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 22:49:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/sec-settles-with-icbc-unit-over-ransomware-attack-imposes-no-fine-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：美元走强抑制多头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-02/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 21:48:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国对中国芯片产业实施新限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-chip-industry-with-new-restrictions-2024-12-02/</link><description>美国周一对中国半导体行业发起了三年来的第三次严厉打击，限制了对包括芯片设备制造商北方华创科技集团在内的 140 家公司的出口。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 19:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-chip-industry-with-new-restrictions-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔能源公司与壳牌签署向中国交付液化天然气的长期协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/qatarenergy-signs-long-term-lng-deal-with-shell-delivery-china-2024-12-02/</link><description>国有卡塔尔能源公司 (QATPE.UL) 与石油和天然气巨头壳牌公司签署了一项长期销售和采购协议，为其提供液化天然气 (LNG) 并运往中国，</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/qatarenergy-signs-long-term-lng-deal-with-shell-delivery-china-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国债券持续上涨，10年期国债收益率跌破2%，创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-relentless-bond-rally-pushes-10-year-yield-below-2-lowest-record-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国10年期国债收益率周一跌破2%，触及历史最低点，打破了心理障碍，因为经济不景气和进一步降息的押注促使投资者转向安全的债券。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-relentless-bond-rally-pushes-10-year-yield-below-2-lowest-record-2024-12-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>